LAB B1 - DEVICE BOOT AND INITIAL CONFIGS

configured root login using system root authentication

configured system host-names for both vSRX devices

configured a login message for both devices

configured an admin user with a super-user class

Enabled SSH and NETCONF

ssh allows both devices to accept ssh connections from client for remote access management
configured security zones trust for both devices ge-0/0/0 interfaces to accept host-inbound-traffic pings

Allows ping to vSRX devices
Assigned IPv4 address for both devices on the g-0/0/0 interfaces

Allows both devices to communicate with each other and ping one another
